1
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:43,119
Is it safe to talk here?

2
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,119
Rest assured.

3
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,000
It's safe here.

4
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,719
I heard

5
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:51,439
Panpan and Xuanzhi
are spies from the court.

6
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:54,479
That's a long story.

7
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:55,600
However,

8
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:56,759
neither of them

9
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:58,079
has done anything to betray us.

10
00:00:58,479 --> 00:00:59,359
That's good.

11
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,719
What do you want to tell me?

12
00:01:09,439 --> 00:01:10,760
We're sisters by blood.

13
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,000
Why be hesitant to talk?

14
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:12,680
Tell me.

15
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,799
Actually,

16
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,480
the Emperor

17
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,959
asked me to come

18
00:01:18,159 --> 00:01:19,959
to steal the military token of Youzhou.

19
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:21,120
What?

20
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,319
This...

21
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,719
Mother was supposed to come,

22
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:29,079
but got detained by the Emperor.

23
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:33,079
Why would he want it?

24
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,840
Youzhou's army follows commanders,

25
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,000
not the token.

26
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:38,439
I don't know.

27
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,319
The Emperor just asked me to steal it.

28
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,760
Don't worry.

29
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,879
I think Li Ya'er has the token.

30
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,239
I'll find a way.

31
00:01:54,963 --> 00:02:00,352
=Treacherous Cases in Shendu=
=Episode 19=

32
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,439
Ling.

33
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,200
What's wrong?

34
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:10,400
There's something I want to discuss.

35
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:11,919
Go ahead.

36
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,479
I need your Youzhou military token.

37
00:02:23,002 --> 00:02:26,912
(Youzhou)

38
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,680
You're just giving it to me?

39
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,680
Even without asking why?

40
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,280
That day, you entrusted me

41
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,560
with the Jinlouzi painting.

42
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,039
Today, I trust you

43
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,479
would use it wisely.

44
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,280
Thank you.

45
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,439
Get some rest.

