♪Darkness looms with impending doom♪

181
00:12:01,652 --> 00:12:07,892
♪A lone hero casts life and death aside♪

182
00:12:08,779 --> 00:12:14,796
♪Sacrificing himself
to right the world's debt♪

183
00:12:15,627 --> 00:12:22,027
♪A long-sealed heart begins to thaw♪

184
00:12:22,368 --> 00:12:28,291
♪Only to lose this forbidden love♪

185
00:12:28,972 --> 00:12:35,735
♪Through any crowd,
I'd find my way to you♪

186
00:12:36,035 --> 00:12:42,244
♪Through every trial and fear,
I'll see you through♪

187
00:12:42,924 --> 00:12:50,139
♪Till dust at last,
within your heart finds rest♪

188
00:12:50,411 --> 00:12:56,316
♪Never to part, whatever betide♪

189
00:12:56,769 --> 00:13:03,412
♪Through any crowd,
I'd find my way to you♪

190
00:13:03,841 --> 00:13:10,080
♪Our love transcends the worldly storm♪

191
00:13:10,561 --> 00:13:19,919
♪Yearning burns as snow melts,
mists clear away♪

192
